@CDCgov But, are they immunized against getting Co-vid as we originally thought was the plan?  No.. 
You also won't be hospitalized or die from Covid if it never gets into your body~ Highly unlikely if wearing a good mask! @POTUS
#MasksWorkFine #Nobreakthroughs #NoSideEffects   #N95Masks

@CDCgov Even if you DO get hospitalized, which is much less likely if vaxxed and/or boosted, your odds are much better of not dying or needing a ventilator.

So way less likely overall.

Get the vax!
